Type: Package
Package: campsismisc
Title: Miscellaneous Utilities for the Campsis Ecosystem
Version: 0.6.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Nicolas", "Luyckx", , "nicolas.luyckx@calvagone.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of utilities extending the 'campsis' ecosystem,
    with a primary focus on sensitivity analysis and uncertainty
    visualization in pharmacometric workflows.  The package provides a
    framework for performing sensitivity analyses by systematically
    varying model parameters (e.g., increased and decreased values) and
    evaluating the resulting impact on model-derived outcomes. It also
    includes functionality to generate forest plots, enabling clear
    visualization of parameter uncertainty and its influence on key
    metrics.  These tools integrate seamlessly with 'campsis',
    'campsismod' and 'campsisnca', supporting efficient simulation,
    analysis and interpretation workflows.
